The paper deals with a matching problem in the context of allocating junior doctors to hospitals, which involves optimization and decision-making. This suggests that it could fall under the categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Game Theory (cs.GT), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Mathematical Optimization (cs.MA).
